WEBVTT

01:34.400 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:52.120 --> 01:57.360
MIE SEDAAP INSTANT NOODLES

01:59.400 --> 02:02.200
NUTS & CANDIED FRUITS

02:02.280 --> 02:07.320
SNACKS

02:57.520 --> 02:58.360
Sorry.

02:59.360 --> 03:00.480
It's okay.

03:06.800 --> 03:08.800
I told you not to run around.
Apologize to this gentleman now.

03:09.320 --> 03:10.720
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

03:44.640 --> 03:45.760
3,646 DAYS

04:13.760 --> 04:15.600
These past days,
I've traveled to many places.

04:17.320 --> 04:19.720
From Nanwu to Yihe, then to Beiyu.

04:22.400 --> 04:24.520
I've been everywhere she might have gone.

04:25.480 --> 04:26.960
And suddenly, I realized…

04:30.640 --> 04:32.600
how small her world was,

04:34.800 --> 04:36.280
like a life trapped in a cage.

04:43.760 --> 04:44.720
Sang Yan.

04:47.720 --> 04:49.040
Dian contacted me today.

04:53.000 --> 04:54.080
What did she say?

04:56.160 --> 04:58.120
Say something! What exactly happened?

04:58.200 --> 04:59.480
Don't panic.

05:00.000 --> 05:01.520
She just told me she's safe.

05:01.600 --> 05:03.520
She didn't tell me where she was.

05:16.840 --> 05:18.480
I really wish she left suddenly…

05:19.760 --> 05:20.920
just to get rid of me.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.360
What do you mean by that?

05:25.440 --> 05:27.520
Maybe in those six years away from us,

05:30.520 --> 05:32.200
she bore a lot on her own.

05:33.880 --> 05:34.920
Now, leaving again,

05:36.360 --> 05:38.680
she probably just wants
to shoulder it alone once again.

05:46.520 --> 05:49.160
Sometimes, I get mad
about the time she was gone.

05:50.880 --> 05:53.280
But who ever thought
about what she went through?

05:54.800 --> 05:56.560
What was on her mind back then?

06:00.040 --> 06:01.840
Now, I'm kind of mad at myself

06:01.920 --> 06:04.080
for not finding her
and asking her back then.

06:11.360 --> 06:12.800
Is she now…

06:15.880 --> 06:17.360
watching the same night view?

06:41.600 --> 06:45.880
So, Hong Kong has a view just like Nanwu.

07:22.160 --> 07:25.360
Hello, Miss Sang. Please come in.

07:25.440 --> 07:28.000
I'll arrange the innermost room for you.

07:28.080 --> 07:29.520
It gets better sunlight.

07:41.560 --> 07:45.440
THAT PAINFUL MEMORY

07:45.520 --> 07:48.840
SIX YEARS AGO, BEIYU

07:48.920 --> 07:50.320
Yifan, come in.

07:50.400 --> 07:51.920
- Put your things here.
- You'll be staying in this room.

07:52.000 --> 07:53.240
- Come.
- Come on. Go in.

07:56.960 --> 07:58.680
It's such a mess. Wen Ming!

07:59.200 --> 08:00.560
Come here, now!

08:02.320 --> 08:04.480
Didn't I tell you before
to clean up this room?

08:04.560 --> 08:07.720
- I had to study!
- Study? You?

08:07.800 --> 08:09.200
You weren't this serious when you took
your college entrance exams.

08:09.280 --> 08:10.800
And now you're suddenly a scholar?

08:10.880 --> 08:13.040
It's okay. I'll clean it up myself.

08:14.080 --> 08:16.600
All right then.
Shuangjiang, clean this place up yourself.

08:17.120 --> 08:18.720
- And you…
- Move.

08:21.080 --> 08:22.440
Wen Ming, come here.

08:22.520 --> 08:23.520
Get over here!

08:24.360 --> 08:25.600
I told you to tidy the room,
and you didn't.

08:25.680 --> 08:27.400
- You did it on purpose, didn't you?
- I…

08:27.480 --> 08:28.360
Enough.

08:28.440 --> 08:30.800
At least save your son some dignity
in front of outsiders.

08:30.880 --> 08:33.320
Fine, you surely know
how to save him face.

08:33.400 --> 08:34.720
I hate to criticize you,

08:35.720 --> 08:37.559
but didn't you agree to this before?

08:37.640 --> 08:39.080
You took their money, didn't you?

08:39.880 --> 08:42.080
If she's staying here, what's wrong
with me charging a little for it?

08:42.159 --> 08:44.680
I can't even complain a little? Honestly!

08:44.760 --> 08:46.400
Fine, you're always right.

08:46.480 --> 08:48.000
- This is all your fault.
- Fine, blame me.

08:48.080 --> 08:49.440
All you two do is argue.

08:51.560 --> 08:53.720
Unbelievable. Be gentle!
He's your own son!

08:53.800 --> 08:54.920
Enough. Hurry up.

08:55.000 --> 08:56.080
Let's get to work.

08:56.160 --> 08:57.320
- Help carry this for us.
- Alright.

08:57.400 --> 08:59.200
Here, give me those two bags.
Give them to me.

09:02.080 --> 09:03.640
Put them on me.

09:03.720 --> 09:05.520
- Aren't they heavy?
- It's fine. Don't worry.

09:16.920 --> 09:18.800
Wen Ming is about
to graduate from college.

09:19.600 --> 09:21.440
Help him find a job.

09:21.960 --> 09:23.760
Sis, I'm just an office worker.

09:23.840 --> 09:25.520
I'm not in HR.

09:25.600 --> 09:26.920
How am I supposed to arrange anything?

09:30.640 --> 09:33.200
Look at the time! You're still not up?

09:33.280 --> 09:34.800
Hurry. Get out here.

09:36.520 --> 09:39.960
Come on, quickly!
Why are you so lazy, girl? Seriously.

09:40.040 --> 09:41.480
Get moving. Come on!

09:44.960 --> 09:47.280
Hurry! What are you afraid of? Come on.

09:47.880 --> 09:49.760
This is your Uncle Che.
Say hello to Uncle Che.

09:49.840 --> 09:52.680
Hello, Uncle Che. Sorry for the trouble.

09:52.760 --> 09:53.960
No need to be so formal.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.960
Just treat this as your own home.

09:57.080 --> 10:00.360
Come. Sit down and eat.
Ming, go get a chair for her.

10:06.760 --> 10:07.600
Here.

10:07.680 --> 10:08.920
Thank you.

10:10.560 --> 10:13.280
You just brought a chair?
Couldn't you grab a bowl, too?

10:14.280 --> 10:15.680
What are you waiting for? Go!

10:21.560 --> 10:25.160
Listen, your Uncle Che
writes in his spare time.

10:25.240 --> 10:28.240
Maybe one day,
he'll be a bestselling author.

10:28.320 --> 10:29.800
Don't talk nonsense, sis.

10:29.880 --> 10:31.840
No need to be polite. It's true.

10:36.160 --> 10:37.040
Oh, right…

10:37.560 --> 10:39.440
If you have any questions
about your studies,

10:39.520 --> 10:40.840
you can ask him.

10:40.920 --> 10:43.520
Just don't bother him too much.
You hear me?

10:45.160 --> 10:46.960
Eat up! The dishes are getting cold.

10:50.320 --> 10:51.400
Thank you.

10:52.040 --> 10:54.080
Hurry and eat the egg. It's getting cold.

10:56.040 --> 10:57.920
Yifan, eat the egg. Here.

11:45.240 --> 11:47.200
- Uncle Che.
- Shuangjiang.

11:47.720 --> 11:49.920
Sorry. I didn't mean to disturb you.

11:54.280 --> 11:55.320
You're studying?

11:57.680 --> 11:59.840
You never come to ask for help.

12:00.360 --> 12:01.440
Do you know all this?

12:14.280 --> 12:16.480
Now that you've moved in, we're family.

12:21.920 --> 12:23.000
No need to be so polite.

12:28.160 --> 12:30.680
I'm exhausted.
You carry the rest of the stuff.

12:30.760 --> 12:32.360
I need to sleep early.

12:36.520 --> 12:38.040
Alright, I won't bother you then.

12:39.000 --> 12:40.360
I live right across from you.

12:40.440 --> 12:43.720
If you need help, just come find me.

12:44.680 --> 12:45.760
Alright?

12:47.000 --> 12:48.240
Get some rest.

13:10.040 --> 13:11.440
You're back, sis. Brother-in-law.

13:21.600 --> 13:24.400
It's so late. You… You're still up?

13:24.480 --> 13:27.120
I just got up to use the bathroom
and checked on Shuangjiang's schoolwork.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.520
I'm heading to bed now.

14:42.760 --> 14:43.920
Why did you bring me here?

14:44.800 --> 14:46.800
If you have nowhere else
to practice dancing, just…

14:46.880 --> 14:48.280
make do here.

14:50.600 --> 14:51.840
Thank you.

14:57.360 --> 14:58.800
Everyone, let me say a few words.

14:59.800 --> 15:02.040
The college entrance exam
is coming up soon.

15:02.120 --> 15:04.360
Choosing the right school
is just as important.

15:04.440 --> 15:08.960
So, make sure to carefully check
past enrollment records and trends.

15:09.040 --> 15:12.560
Find a university and major you like,

15:12.640 --> 15:15.360
and work hard toward that goal.

15:15.880 --> 15:18.120
If there's anything you don't understand,
you can ask me,

15:18.200 --> 15:20.560
or discuss it with your family.

15:20.640 --> 15:23.360
- Got it?
- Got it!

15:23.880 --> 15:24.920
Alright, keep working.

15:30.760 --> 15:32.600
I will definitely get
into Nanwu University.

15:34.880 --> 15:36.840
And I believe you will, too.

15:38.880 --> 15:40.240
Then, let's make a promise.

15:40.760 --> 15:43.320
We'll work hard together
and get into Nanwu University together.

15:56.000 --> 15:57.560
I want to go back to Nanwu.

15:58.360 --> 16:00.520
This time, let me go back for you.

16:10.480 --> 16:13.200
GOAL: NANWU UNIVERSITY!

16:19.120 --> 16:21.000
I'll go see you tomorrow.

16:23.240 --> 16:25.760
I'm heading back to Nanwu soon.
Don't come over.

16:31.640 --> 16:32.680
When?

16:37.280 --> 16:41.240
Um… Wait until
the admission letter arrives, I guess.

16:42.920 --> 16:44.640
That'll be in July.

16:45.720 --> 16:47.720
I've made you take
a special trip every time.

16:47.800 --> 16:48.920
It's such a hassle.

16:50.200 --> 16:51.360
How about this?

16:51.440 --> 16:54.560
When the results come out,
I'll go over instead.

16:55.560 --> 16:56.640
Alright.

16:58.240 --> 16:59.320
Good night.

17:02.600 --> 17:04.079
NANWU UNIVERSITY
UNDERGRADUATE ADMISSIONS GUIDE

17:19.920 --> 17:21.560
HAVE YOU BEEN TOO BUSY WITH STUDYING?
YOU BARELY REPLY TO MY MESSAGES

17:21.640 --> 17:22.880
WEN YIFAN: I'M FINE. EVERYTHING'S GOOD

17:22.960 --> 17:24.520
YOU SHOULD FOCUS ON STUDYING
DON'T MESS UP NOW

17:24.599 --> 17:26.920
ONCE I GET MY ACCEPTANCE LETTER TO
NANWU UNIVERSITY, I'M COMING TO SEE YOU!

17:27.000 --> 17:28.200
Jiang.

17:35.200 --> 17:36.320
Jiang.

17:47.960 --> 17:49.160
Jiang.

17:51.360 --> 17:53.040
What's the matter, Uncle Che?

17:53.120 --> 17:55.440
Well… Can you come help me with something?

18:09.760 --> 18:11.560
- What is it?
- Your aunt just called.

18:11.640 --> 18:13.800
She said they ran out
of seasoning at the stall.

18:13.880 --> 18:14.920
She asked me to find some
and bring it over.

18:15.840 --> 18:18.120
There's too much stuff here.
Can you help me out?

18:24.080 --> 18:25.560
What seasoning?

18:26.760 --> 18:27.600
Chicken powder.

18:37.360 --> 18:38.880
There's only tissue paper in here.

18:38.960 --> 18:40.520
Check the top shelf.

18:40.600 --> 18:42.920
They always put things in random places.

18:46.440 --> 18:48.360
Right. Is there any in this bag?

18:49.760 --> 18:51.080
- What are you doing?
- Nothing.

18:51.160 --> 18:53.640
- Keep looking. Check the bottom shelf.
- Find it yourself, Uncle Che.

18:53.720 --> 18:55.160
Come on. Help me find it.

18:55.240 --> 18:57.040
- Let go of me!
- What's that noise?

18:57.120 --> 18:58.200
What are you arguing about?

19:02.720 --> 19:05.040
Sis, brother-in-law.
You're back so early? No business today?

19:05.120 --> 19:06.600
Uncle Wen.

19:06.680 --> 19:08.000
- Uncle Che…
- Jiang…

19:08.080 --> 19:09.960
Uh, go rest in your room for a while.

19:10.040 --> 19:12.360
Hurry. Go on.

19:13.080 --> 19:16.160
Shuangjiang, listen to your aunt.
Go to your room and do your homework.

19:16.240 --> 19:18.760
Look, we run a business all day long.
We're so busy.

19:19.280 --> 19:20.680
We're barely home.

19:20.760 --> 19:23.360
So… you need to be obedient
to your Uncle Che.

19:31.160 --> 19:33.040
Alright, that's enough. Go to your room.

19:33.680 --> 19:35.400
Go on. Drink some water later.

19:36.120 --> 19:37.560
- Here.
- Thanks, Jiang.

19:37.640 --> 19:38.720
Go on now.

19:45.520 --> 19:48.040
Well… I'm heading out.

20:15.000 --> 20:16.040
Clean up this mess.

20:16.720 --> 20:18.640
Okay. You rest up first.

20:31.320 --> 20:34.560
No matter what,
a girl living alone is too dangerous.

20:35.080 --> 20:37.680
No way. Let's stop
talking about moving out.

20:38.520 --> 20:42.960
But I'm really scared, Mom.
Please take me home, okay?

20:43.040 --> 20:45.800
I'm really scared!

20:46.320 --> 20:48.320
I'm begging you…

20:48.400 --> 20:50.280
Don't cry. Listen to me.

20:50.360 --> 20:53.480
I'll talk to your Uncle Wen. Don't worry.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.040
I have to hang up now.

21:18.640 --> 21:19.800
FINAL EXAM CRAM

21:19.880 --> 21:21.320
Alright, class dismissed.

21:22.120 --> 21:25.720
Go home and get some rest now.
Come back tomorrow for more prep.

21:47.920 --> 21:49.000
Miss.

21:49.080 --> 21:51.880
Night study is over. Hurry home.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.040
Stay safe on your way back.

22:34.040 --> 22:36.920
AFTER THE COLLEGE ENTRANCE EXAM

23:25.800 --> 23:26.960
If you keep this up,
I'm calling the police.

23:27.680 --> 23:29.280
Call the police?

23:29.360 --> 23:31.040
This injury is proof you tried to kill me.

23:31.120 --> 23:33.640
- You really dare to report me?
- You've been harassing me all this time!

23:33.720 --> 23:36.800
I can just tell them
that you tried to steal my money.

23:36.880 --> 23:38.440
Who do you think they'll believe?

23:55.480 --> 23:56.600
Don't come any closer! I'll scream!

24:02.320 --> 24:04.680
Scream? Do you want everyone to know?

24:05.200 --> 24:06.840
Do you think anyone
will marry you later, Jiang?

24:06.920 --> 24:10.360
Do you even realize how shameful,
how humiliating this is?

24:11.400 --> 24:12.640
- Don't scream!
- Uncle Wen!

24:12.720 --> 24:14.320
Uncle Wen! Help me!

24:24.840 --> 24:26.200
Come here.

24:26.760 --> 24:28.880
Don't touch me! I'll jump!

24:37.160 --> 24:39.200
- Yifan!
- De!

24:39.280 --> 24:40.400
- De!
- Yifan!

24:40.480 --> 24:41.920
- What's going on here?
- De.

24:42.000 --> 24:43.320
- Are you alright?
- De, say something!

24:43.400 --> 24:44.560
You're not dead, right, De?

24:44.640 --> 24:45.560
- Yifan!
- Say something!

24:47.800 --> 24:48.640
I need to call the police…

24:50.080 --> 24:52.080
You're not dead? You scared me to death!

24:52.160 --> 24:54.040
What are you waiting for?
Come help already!

24:54.120 --> 24:56.320
Get them up first!

24:57.080 --> 24:58.840
Look at your daughter.

24:58.920 --> 25:02.080
I worked so hard raising her for you,
letting her stay in my house.

25:02.160 --> 25:03.200
And what did she do?

25:03.280 --> 25:05.720
She… She wants to throw
my brother in jail!

25:06.560 --> 25:08.080
I'm sorry! Please, don't be mad.

25:08.160 --> 25:10.600
Don't be mad?
What did my brother do wrong?

25:10.680 --> 25:13.440
He was just drunk
and went into the wrong room!

25:13.520 --> 25:15.760
Look, how heartless she is!

25:15.840 --> 25:17.640
My brother didn't do anything to her,
and yet…

25:17.720 --> 25:18.960
she let him fall and break his leg,

25:19.040 --> 25:22.080
and now she wants to slap him
with… a rape charge!

25:22.680 --> 25:24.040
How can you throw around
accusations like that?

25:24.120 --> 25:26.800
- Calm down.
- It really pains me!

25:26.880 --> 25:28.200
I'll go talk to her.

25:28.280 --> 25:32.600
Jiang, did you misunderstand something?

25:32.680 --> 25:36.520
Your aunt's brother is a good man.
He would never do something like this.

25:36.600 --> 25:38.920
- Why are you all arguing?
- Don't overthink it, okay?

25:39.560 --> 25:41.040
If you want to argue, take it outside.

25:41.120 --> 25:43.400
- Go argue somewhere else.
- We're not arguing.

25:47.280 --> 25:48.840
Are you alright?

25:48.920 --> 25:52.640
We can go to the police station.
It's quieter there.

25:52.720 --> 25:54.280
Let's go make a statement.

25:54.360 --> 25:58.560
Go on. Tell the officer
everything that happened.

25:59.080 --> 26:01.320
A guardian can accompany her.
You can come along.

26:01.840 --> 26:02.960
I…

26:04.240 --> 26:07.400
I have to go now.
Uncle Zheng drove me here.

26:07.480 --> 26:09.120
- He's still waiting outside.
- Mom…

26:09.200 --> 26:10.600
- I can't let him wait.
- I'm begging you…

26:10.680 --> 26:11.760
He has work tomorrow.

26:11.840 --> 26:13.560
- Please…
- You can't just leave now.

26:13.640 --> 26:14.960
Your daughter's trouble isn't solved yet.

26:15.040 --> 26:18.840
Help me! Please don't abandon me again.

26:18.920 --> 26:20.480
Call me if you need anything.
I'm leaving now.

26:20.560 --> 26:22.520
"We'll talk later?" What do you mean?

26:22.600 --> 26:24.120
You're really leaving?

26:32.800 --> 26:33.960
Can we go now?

26:49.440 --> 26:50.600
Your foot is hurt.

26:52.920 --> 26:54.000
Take care.

27:14.400 --> 27:15.480
It feels like the rain in Beiyu

27:16.480 --> 27:18.560
has soaked into my bones.

27:19.720 --> 27:21.160
No matter where I run,

27:21.880 --> 27:24.120
I can't escape that rainy day.

28:06.240 --> 28:07.920
Excuse me. Dian!

28:15.760 --> 28:16.720
Dian!

28:22.920 --> 28:24.280
Is that you, Dian?

28:43.800 --> 28:47.520
The number you're dialing is powered off.
Please try again later.

29:01.040 --> 29:02.240
Hello, Xiang Lang.

29:02.760 --> 29:04.120
Hello, Qiao. Are you busy?

29:05.120 --> 29:06.320
Not really.

29:07.920 --> 29:10.000
I didn't go back
for the last New Year holiday.

29:12.240 --> 29:15.440
Such a pity.
Our Nanwu Trio didn't get to reunite.

29:16.280 --> 29:17.360
How have you been?

29:18.000 --> 29:21.160
Are you and Dian doing okay recently?

29:24.320 --> 29:25.440
What's wrong?

29:25.960 --> 29:27.840
Did… something happen to Dian?

29:28.680 --> 29:31.200
She… ran away from home.

29:35.120 --> 29:37.400
I think… I just saw Dian.

29:38.120 --> 29:39.320
Where?

29:55.640 --> 29:58.680
Welcome! Looking for a meal?

30:36.440 --> 30:39.200
You're thinking of her, too, aren't you?

30:54.760 --> 30:57.400
Sang Yan… I…

30:57.920 --> 30:59.400
I don't deserve to ask
for your forgiveness

30:59.480 --> 31:00.640
for leaving without telling you.

31:01.800 --> 31:04.240
Not last time, and not this time either.

31:05.760 --> 31:07.600
I don't expect you to understand.

31:08.280 --> 31:11.800
But please believe me.
I had no choice but to leave.

31:13.320 --> 31:15.320
Don't miss me. Don't look for me.

31:35.680 --> 31:36.880
That rumor…

31:39.520 --> 31:40.760
was meant to make you believe it.

32:18.720 --> 32:20.680
MISSED CALL

32:20.760 --> 32:24.160
HOW ARE YOU?
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU

32:24.240 --> 32:27.120
GOOD NIGHT
DON'T FORGET TO EAT

32:27.200 --> 32:29.480
MISSED CALL
I MISS YOU

32:34.800 --> 32:36.560
I've read your letter.

32:38.400 --> 32:39.760
Send me another one.

32:54.200 --> 32:56.120
SIX MONTHS LATER

32:56.200 --> 32:58.040
BING'S TEA HOUSE

33:05.840 --> 33:06.840
Wen Yifan!

33:15.440 --> 33:16.840
Why are you here?

33:17.560 --> 33:19.200
I'm studying here and working part-time.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.520
- Aren't you exhausted?
- It's fine.

33:21.600 --> 33:22.880
Sit down. Let's talk.

33:24.080 --> 33:26.040
- I haven't finished cleaning up yet.
- I'll help you.

33:26.120 --> 33:27.840
No need! No need, really.

33:30.680 --> 33:31.560
Just sit down and chat.

33:35.800 --> 33:36.960
It's been a long time.

33:37.480 --> 33:38.520
How have you guys been?

33:38.600 --> 33:41.760
Our dance training school
is still running.

33:41.840 --> 33:43.720
- Come visit when you have time.
- Alright.

33:47.720 --> 33:50.480
Wash the dishes!
You still have time to chat?

33:51.560 --> 33:53.040
- Take your time. I'll get back to work.
- Unbelievable!

33:57.880 --> 33:58.920
Thank you.

35:46.200 --> 35:48.480
You're out of wine.
Let me buy you a drink.

35:48.560 --> 35:50.000
No need. I should go.

35:50.080 --> 35:51.280
It's fine. Don't be so polite.

35:51.360 --> 35:53.240
Hey, get her a drink. Put it on my tab.

35:53.760 --> 35:55.800
- Got it.
- Really, I don't need one.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.320
Where are you going
in the middle of the day?

36:08.240 --> 36:09.280
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

36:09.360 --> 36:10.680
What happened?

36:10.760 --> 36:12.640
That guy was harassing a female customer.

36:12.720 --> 36:14.480
Our boss took him away.

36:30.280 --> 36:31.880
Zhuo. He!

36:40.720 --> 36:42.920
Fuck you.

36:43.000 --> 36:45.800
If I hadn't come looking for you,
you still dared to show up here?

36:45.880 --> 36:47.040
Huh?

36:47.120 --> 36:50.120
I'm just here for a drink.
Did I do something to you?

36:52.640 --> 36:55.640
Don't ever let me see you again. Got it?

36:55.720 --> 36:57.720
Alright. Okay, I get it.

36:57.800 --> 36:58.880
I get it.

37:22.440 --> 37:23.640
I understand now.

37:25.920 --> 37:28.400
I touched your little girl before,
so now you're mad, right?

37:29.080 --> 37:31.880
Come on. We're all men here.
You should understand, right?

37:34.400 --> 37:35.440
She's just an insignificant woman.

37:36.240 --> 37:40.240
I almost had her.
Want me to tell you how it felt?

38:31.520 --> 38:32.720
Come on.

38:33.480 --> 38:35.720
Is that all you've got?

38:41.800 --> 38:45.080
Jun! He! Yan is here!

38:49.720 --> 38:51.960
- Boss.
- Boss. How are you?

38:53.680 --> 38:55.000
Call an ambulance for him.

38:56.120 --> 38:57.240
Hurry up!

39:10.000 --> 39:15.120
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

39:36.840 --> 39:39.040
Don't you think

39:39.880 --> 39:41.680
watching horror movies
helps you forget things?

39:45.720 --> 39:48.200
No other genre works?

39:48.800 --> 39:50.600
Seems like horror movies work best.

39:58.640 --> 40:02.120
Hello, sir. The movie is over.
Please exit this way.

43:12.960 --> 43:14.120
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

43:14.200 --> 43:15.240
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
